Dakota County Office of Geographic Information Systems

Every roadway in Dakota County has a street address range assigned to each side of the street. The street address map can be used to map either single or multiple street address locations. The street address database can be used to map the location of an address when typed into the computer, or read a list of addresses from a file and display their many locations.
